# DocsBot API credentials are stored in Apps Script Script Properties,
# not in environment variables. Use the sheet menu: DocsBot Audit > Setup API Key.
#
# For reference, you will need:
# - DocsBot API key (Bearer token from DocsBot dashboard)
# - Team ID (from DocsBot URL or API)
# - Bot ID (from DocsBot URL or API)
#
# Team ID and Bot ID are set in Config.js in this project.
